"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-boxing-1956436-Delicious-Orie-WWE-Olympics-boxing\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Olympic boxer Delicious Orie admits he is considering walking away from boxing after receiving an offer to jointhe WWE.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9998513476700205, \"rank\": 0.00014339689427576456, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Super-heavyweight Orie, 27, won gold medals at the European Championships and Commonwealth Games beforerepresenting Team GB in the Olympics in Paristhis summer.\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 174, \"end\": 196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9998935393130591, \"rank\": 7.554684203198947e-05, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9581288126304628, \"rank\": 0.024964035012764726, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9994799958841486, \"rank\": 0.0004218227181156936, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wouldlose in the first round by a contentious split decisionto former world silver medallist Davit Chaloyan.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It seemed certain that Orie, who wasborn in Russia and moved to Wolverhampton aged seven,would turn professional and lead the next generation of British heavyweight prospects.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.7563654678571463, \"rank\": 0.3123483675693631, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 461, \"end\": 474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wolverhampton\", \"score\": 0.8439098891821507, \"rank\": 0.1578559139937479, \"text\": \"Wolverhampton\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wolverhampton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wolverhampton\"}, {\"begin\": 542, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9999997683005672, \"rank\": 2.313878158078919e-07, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 6ft 6in heavy hitter admits his career path is in doubt after receiving an offer fromthe WWE- the world-leading professional wrestling promotion - with proposals also on the table from leading boxing promoters.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been invited to potentially join the WWE, as mad as that sounds,\\\" Orie toldToe 2 Toe.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9998513476700205, \"rank\": 0.00014339689427576456, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just went out there go and see what it's all about.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a fantastic experience, I learned so much over the few days that I was there and it's definitely something that I have got on the table as an option.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's real.\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I got the message over the Olympic Games and at the time I wasn't really looking at my messages, I was purely focused on the games.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, I was on holiday and that's when I slowly started to reply and I saw the message.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I initially thought it was a scam and then I looked more into it and it was legit.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They said 'We see your potential and we would like to work with you'.\\\"\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie, who has a 29-9 record as an amateur, was flown to the WWE Performance Centre in Florida where he learned the ropes and worked on a finishing move called the \\\"Delicious Haymaker'.\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9998513476700205, \"rank\": 0.00014339689427576456, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}, {\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9999852875973815, \"rank\": 1.0187590818205734e-05, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But deciding his future is serious business and he will not to rush the process.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"Ultimately, I have a decision to make and it's not something I am taking lightly.\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's something I have really got to take my time on because at the end of the day, this will shape my whole career.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be huge.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am in a stage now where I am waiting for the offers, including the WWE, looking at the contracts and seeing what's expected of me from the [boxing] promoters and the WWE side.\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9998513476700205, \"rank\": 0.00014339689427576456, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}, {\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"score\": 0.9998513476700205, \"rank\": 0.00014339689427576456, \"text\": \"WWE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WWE\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just want to have all the options on the table so I can make my full decision because whatever it is I decide to do, I am going to put my 100 per cent commitment [into it] and I will sacrifice everything to be the best at that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2551, \"end\": 2564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3005706623458446e-14, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2600, \"end\": 2613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3005706623458446e-14, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"